| **PEG parser** | `generation_prompt` literal + `content(rest())` — straightforward content capture, no tool-call or reasoning paths needed for this format |
| **No header change** | `common_chat_try_specialized_template` is the only public entry point; the new static function is an internal implementation detail, matching every other handler |

